6 BE IT RESOLVED by the Legislature of Louisiana that Joint Rule 23 of the Joint
7 Rules of the Senate and House of Representatives is hereby adopted to read as follows:
8 Joint Rule No. 23. Required disclosure on certain notices of local or special laws
9 A notice of the intent to introduce a bill to enact a local or special law as
10 required by Article III, Section 13(A) of the Constitution of Louisiana that is caused
11 to be published by a person other than a member of the legislature shall include the
